name: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Neal Stuart SPECTOR.

court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

parties: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Neal Stuart SPECTOR.

opinions.text: Neal Stuart SPECTOR, of New York, New York, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.

casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Neal Stuart SPECTOR.
No. D-2815.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 6, 2014.
Opinion
